        <updateDate>2007-10-27T14:34:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Providing Tax Fairness for Service Members and Veterans Act of 2007 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to extend through 2011: (1) the taxpayer election to include combat pay as earned income for purposes of computing the earned income tax credit; and (2) eligibility of veterans for mortgage financing without regard to first-time homebuyer requirements. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
